text: Rheinwald is a new municipality in Hinterrhein in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. On 1 January 2019 the municipalities Hinterrhein, Nufenen and Splügen joined to become the new municipality Rheinwald. == References == == Other websites == * Official website of the municipality of Rheinwald Category:Municipalities in Hinterrhein Category:2010s establishments in Switzerland Category:2019 establishments in Europe
